---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Privacy Policy | ProxyFAQs"
  description="Our commitment to protecting your privacy and data."
>
  <section class="bg-secondary-50 py-12">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-4xl">
      <div class="card">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="text-secondary-500 mb-8">Last updated: January 3, 2026</p>

        <div class="prose-custom">
          <h2>Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            ProxyFAQs ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy
            Policy explains how we collect, use, and share information about you when you use our
            website and services.
          </p>

          <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
          <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Chat messages you send to our AI assistant</li>
            <li>Search queries you submit</li>
            <li>Page views and navigation patterns</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>IP address (anonymized)</li>
            <li>Browser type and version</li>
            <li>Device information</li>
            <li>Referral source</li>
            <li>Pages visited and time spent on pages</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>Cookies and Tracking</h3>
          <p>We use minimal cookies to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Remember your chat session</li>
            <li>Track anonymous analytics via Umami (privacy-focused)</li>
            <li>No third-party advertising cookies</li>
            <li>No cross-site tracking</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use collected information to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and improve our services</li>
            <li>Answer your questions via AI chat</li>
            <li>Analyze usage patterns to improve content</li>
            <li>Prevent abuse and ensure security</li>
            <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
          <p>We do NOT sell your personal information. We may share data with:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>AI Provider (VectorEngine):</strong> Chat messages are sent to VectorEngine API
              for processing
            </li>
            <li><strong>Analytics (Umami):</strong> Anonymized usage statistics</li>
            <li><strong>Hosting (Cloudflare):</strong> Technical data for content delivery</li>
            <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> When required by law or to protect rights</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Data Retention</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Chat sessions: 30 days</li>
            <li>Analytics data: 12 months</li>
            <li>Search logs: 90 days</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Your Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access your personal information</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Opt out of analytics tracking</li>
            <li>Disable cookies in your browser</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p>
            Our site contains links to proxy providers and external resources. We are not
            responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. Some links are affiliate
            links, which are clearly marked.
          </p>

          <h2 id="affiliate-disclosure">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="font-semibold text-secondary-800">
            Transparency is important to us. Here is our complete affiliate disclosure:
          </p>
          <h3>What Are Affiliate Links?</h3>
          <p>
            Affiliate links are special URLs that allow us to earn a small commission when you make
            a purchase through them. This commission comes from the seller, not from you.
          </p>
          <h3>Our Affiliate Relationships</h3>
          <p>We participate in affiliate programs with the following types of companies:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Proxy service providers (residential, datacenter, mobile proxies)</li>
            <li>Web scraping tools and platforms</li>
            <li>VPN providers</li>
            <li>Related technology services</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>How This Affects You</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>Cost to you:</strong> Zero. Affiliate links do not increase the price you pay.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Our recommendations:</strong> We only recommend services we have personally tested
              or thoroughly researched.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Editorial independence:</strong> Affiliate relationships do not influence our reviews
              or rankings.
            </li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Identification of Affiliate Links</h3>
          <p>Affiliate links on our site are identified in the following ways:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Banner disclosures at the top of pages containing affiliate links</li>
            <li>Inline disclosures within chat responses that include affiliate recommendations</li>
            <li>Sidebar notices on provider comparison pages</li>
            <li>Footer disclosure on all pages</li>
          </ul>
          <h3>Our Policy</h3>
          <p>
            We comply with the Federal Trade Commission's (FTC) "Endorsement Guides" regarding the
            use of testimonials and endorsements in advertising. Our affiliate relationships never
            influence our editorial content, and we maintain honest and unbiased reviews.
          </p>

          <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our service is not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect
            information from children under 13.
          </p>

          <h2>International Users</h2>
          <p>
            Our service is hosted globally via Cloudflare. By using ProxyFAQs, you consent to the
            transfer and processing of your information in accordance with this policy.
          </p>

          <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will post any changes on this
            page.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
